          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Term:
          <ol>
            <li>Preterm/Term/Post-term; Gestational age in weeks</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Mode of delivery:
          <ol>
            <li>Normal vaginal/</li>
            <li>Assisted (Forceps/Vacuum)/</li>
            <ol>
              <li>Indication </li>
            </ol>
