            </ol>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Duration of labor:
          <ol>
            <li>Stage 1,</li>
            <li>&nbsp;Stage 2</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Nature of amniotic fluid:
          <ol>
            <li>Clear/</li>
            <li>Meconium stained/</li>
            <li>Foul smelling</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Immediate cry after birth:
          <ol>
            <li>Yes/</li>
            <li>No; </li>
            <ol>
              <li>time taken</li>
            </ol>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>APGAR score:
          <ol>
            <li>At 1 min, </li>
            <li>5 min</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Birth weight:
          <ol>
            <li>kg</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Any birth injuries:
          <ol>
            <li>Details</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p></p>
      <p><strong>Postnatal History:</strong> </p>
      <ol>
        <li>Condition at birth:
          <ol>
            <li>Vigorous/Crying/Limp/Cyanosed</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Breastfeeding initiated:
          <ol>
            <li>Within 1 hour/Later</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Neonatal problems:
          <ol>
            <li>e.g., Jaundice, Sepsis, RDS, Hypoglycemia, Convulsions, NICU
              admission - duration, reason</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Medications given:
          <ol>
            <li>e.g., Vitamin K</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Rooming-in:
          <ol>
            <li>Yes/No</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Date of discharge:
          <ol>
            <li>Details</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p></p>
    </div>
