    <h3 class="section-title">XI. REVIEW OF SYSTEMS (ROS)</h3>
    <p class="detail-prompt">(Brief inquiry about symptoms in other systems not
      covered in HPI)</p>
    <div class="sub-list">
      <p><strong>General:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Fever</li>
        <li>Weight loss/gain</li>
        <li>Fatigue</li>
        <li>Irritability</li>
        <li>Activity level</li>
      </ol>
      <p><strong>Skin:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Rashes</li>
        <li>Itching</li>
        <li>Dryness</li>
        <li>Color changes</li>
        <li>New lesions</li>
      </ol>
