      <ol>
        <li>Seizures</li>
        <li>Headache</li>
        <li>Loss of consciousness</li>
        <li>Weakness</li>
        <li>Abnormal movements</li>
        <li>Changes in sensation</li>
        <li>Coordination problems</li>
        <li>Changes in behavior/mood</li>
      </ol>
